data.description: 2 bedroom, 11/2 bath, 2 story condo with loft area in highly desired Springwood Condo Assoc. This unit offers a spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliance, quartz countertops and 1st floor laundry/mechanical room. Dining room has table area with sliding door access to patio for outside grilling or just chilling! All flooring on main level is wood laminate. Upper level has a carpeted master bedroom with walk-in closet. Loft area can be used as an office, play area, or 3rd bedroom. 2nd bedroom has carpeting & double closets. Main bath has just been fitted & refinished with a walk-in shower. Main floor area has a 1/2 bath and foyer. 2 car attached heated garage. Some handicap accessibility. Chair lift is negotiable. Ramp in garage. HVAC is 4yrs. Roof recently replaced by association 5yrs. Taxes reflect senior exemption.
